    13	| **C#/.NET** | `csharp/` | Structural + coupling + security, dotnet-based dep analysis |
    14	| **Dart** | `dart/` | Flutter-aware, pubspec integration, test coverage mapping |
    15	| **GDScript** | `gdscript/` | Godot scene-aware, tree-sitter phases, shared framework helpers |
    16	| **Go** | `go/` | golangci-lint + go vet adapters, regex function extraction, test coverage mapping |
